column1: Uchi//// We had a variety of sushi and the Jar Jar Duck. All the flavors blew my mind. The Jar Jar Duck was delicious
column2: the foie gras sushi was super indulgent. The Machi Cure was one of my favorites. There was a Wyagu beef sushi
column3: which I'm usually not a fan of beef
column4: but it was mind blowing. We got the lemon gelato and fried milk for dessert which were both delicious
column5: though I preferred the fried milk
